# @node-versions: v26.1.0
# @description: Bypass temporal_capi gyp target; inline shim include paths into V8
#
# V8's js-temporal-objects.cc #includes `temporal_rs/*.hpp`. Upstream
# resolves this through the `:temporal_capi` gyp target's
# `direct_dependent_settings.include_dirs`, where temporal_capi is
# defined in `deps/crates/crates.gyp` and points at the diplomat-
# generated headers shipped by the Rust crate `temporal_capi`
# (`<cargo_vendor_dir>/temporal_capi/bindings/cpp/`).
#
# socket-btm ships a hand-written C++ port of temporal_capi (the
# `temporal-infra` package) plus a drop-in shim header layer at
# `packages/temporal-infra/include/temporal_rs/` that exposes the same
# `temporal_rs::*` surface V8 expects but routes everything to the
# C++ port (compiled directly into libnode by patch 004).
#
# This patch sidesteps the `temporal_capi` gyp target entirely. The
# two V8 targets that previously depended on `:temporal_capi`
# (mksnapshot, v8_base_without_compiler) now declare the shim include
# paths inline via `include_dirs`. Result:
#
#   1. `deps/crates/crates.gyp` becomes orphan — nothing depends on
#      either of its targets (`temporal_capi`, `node_crates`), so gyp
#      doesn't generate ninja rules for them. The rustc/cargo
#      toolchain drops out of the build entirely.
#   2. V8's compile of js-temporal-objects.cc resolves
#      `temporal_rs/Calendar.hpp` via the shim headers at
#      `<src_root>/include/temporal_rs/` (populated by
#      copy-additions.mts from packages/temporal-infra/include/).
#   3. Link of libnode + mksnapshot picks up the temporal-infra C++
#      port symbols from libnode.a (added by patch 004).
#
# Files modified:
# - tools/v8_gypfiles/v8.gyp: 2 dependency-edges swapped for include_dirs
#
--- a/tools/v8_gypfiles/v8.gyp
+++ b/tools/v8_gypfiles/v8.gyp
@@ -316,8 +316,9 @@
           ],
         }],
         ['v8_enable_temporal_support==1 and node_shared_temporal_capi=="false"', {
-          'dependencies': [
-            '../../deps/crates/crates.gyp:temporal_capi',
+          'include_dirs': [
+            '../../include',
+            '../../src',
           ],
         }],
         ['v8_target_arch=="ia32"', {
@@ -1090,8 +1091,9 @@
         ['v8_enable_temporal_support==1', {
           'conditions': [
             ['node_shared_temporal_capi=="false"', {
-              'dependencies': [
-                '../../deps/crates/crates.gyp:temporal_capi',
+              'include_dirs': [
+                '../../include',
+                '../../src',
               ],
             }],
           ],
